    {
      "name": "gRPC API",
      "description": "## Using Postman for gRPC\n1. Create a new **gRPC request** in Postman (New → gRPC Request).\n2. Set the server URL to `{{grpc_host}}` (default `localhost:50051`).\n3. Import `proto/inventory.proto` via **Import a .proto file**.\n4. Select the service method and paste the message JSON below.\n\nThe gRPC server has **reflection enabled**, so Postman can auto-discover methods without importing the `.proto` manually (Server Reflection toggle in Postman).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "CheckStock – MED-001 (Unary)",
          "request": {
            "method": "INVOKE",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sku\": \"MED-001\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpc_host}}/inventory.InventoryService/CheckStock",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": [
                "{{grpc_host}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "inventory.InventoryService",
                "CheckStock"
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Unary RPC** – returns a single `StockResponse` for the given SKU.\n\n**Expected response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"sku\": \"MED-001\",\n  \"medicine_name\": \"Amoxicillin 500mg\",\n  \"quantity\": 1450,\n  \"requires_prescription\": true\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "CheckStock – MED-089 (low-stock item)",
          "request": {
            "method": "INVOKE",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sku\": \"MED-089\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpc_host}}/inventory.InventoryService/CheckStock",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": [
                "{{grpc_host}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "inventory.InventoryService",
                "CheckStock"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Fetches Ibuprofen 200mg – quantity is below the low-stock threshold (12 units)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "CheckStock – NOT_FOUND error",
          "request": {
            "method": "INVOKE",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sku\": \"INVALID-000\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpc_host}}/inventory.InventoryService/CheckStock",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": [
                "{{grpc_host}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "inventory.InventoryService",
                "CheckStock"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Expects a gRPC `NOT_FOUND (5)` status error because the SKU does not exist in the REST API."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "StreamLowStock (Server-Streaming)",
          "request": {
            "method": "INVOKE",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "grpc://{{grpc_host}}/inventory.InventoryService/StreamLowStock",
              "protocol": "grpc",
              "host": [
                "{{grpc_host}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "inventory.InventoryService",
                "StreamLowStock"
              ]
            },
            "description": "**Server-Streaming RPC** – streams one `StockResponse` message per low-stock item.\n\nPostman shows each streamed message in the **Messages** panel as it arrives. The stream closes once the server has sent all items.\n\n**Expected stream (3 messages with default seed data):**\n```\n{ sku: 'MED-089', medicine_name: 'Ibuprofen 200mg',  quantity: 12, requires_prescription: false }\n{ sku: 'MED-102', medicine_name: 'Lisinopril 10mg',  quantity: 5,  requires_prescription: true  }\n{ sku: 'MED-201', medicine_name: 'Cetirizine 10mg',  quantity: 8,  requires_prescription: false }\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
